            <div class="rich-text--base"><p class="lead">Study - 6-in-1 part 2</p><p>A children's study which will guide decisions on future changes to the routine UK immunisation schedule. Two optional doses of a vaccine which helps to prevent chickenpox will be offered in visits to the participants own home.</p></div>

            

    
