            <div class="rich-text--base"><p class="lead" style="text-align: center;" data-mce-style="text-align: center;"><span class="figure image-left" style="width:120px;"><img data-mce-style="float: left;" src="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/images/main/nisec_logo.png/@@images/d65dedde-23ec-4009-a6ac-d16b54bdea54.png" style="float: left;" title="NISEC_logo.png" data-mce-src="resolveuid/920cdae78d6a41ac8399caa0df710c8d/@@images/image/w120" data-copyright-style="inverted" data-src="https://www.ovg.ox.ac.uk/images/main/nisec_logo.png" alt="NISEC_logo.png" /></span></p><p>OVG is proud to lead the National Immunisation Schedule Evaluation Consortium II (NISEC II), a collaboration between a network of Academic Clinical Research groups and the <span>UK Health Security Agenc</span>y.</p></div>

            

    
